NAME

DateTime::Locale::mer - Locale data examples for the Meru (mer) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Meru locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Wairi, 5 Feburuarĩ 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Wetano, 22 Dicemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Jumamosi, 15 Septemba -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feburuarĩ 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Dicemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Septemba -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 FEB 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 DEC 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 SPT -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B

Bhm (h:mm B)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 6:30 B
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9:05 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44 B

Bhms (h:mm:ss B)

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4:44:23 B

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = WTN 09:05:02
